name: Exam Testing Engine File
summary: Learn about .ETE files and view a list of programs that open them.

content: You can open ETE files using Exam Testing Engine software. You can also upload ETE files to VCEConvert.com and convert them to .PDF files using the ETE to PDF online conversion tool.
NOTE: ETE files are similar to .VCE files, which are created by Visual CertExam Suite.
